----------------------------------------
How to Run Examples
----------------------------------------

1. Get a dojo distribution (http://dojotoolkit.org/downloads), and place the dojo,
dijit, and dojox dirs as peers to the examples dir:

cujo/
...cujo/
...examples/
...templates/
...tests/
...dojo/
...dijit/
...dojox/

2. Open any example's index.html file using your favorite browser.

----------------------------------------
Notes on Specific Examples
----------------------------------------

digital-clock - The digital-clock example currently does not run in IE 6-8.